Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:07.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuya-dono...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.83,0:00:09.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:14.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:20.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still a little embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:21.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but would you watch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.85,0:01:55.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:01:59.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:06.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're beanbags.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:08.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:11.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to juggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to juggle three earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:17.95,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs54\c&HB83D41&\pos(643,96)}Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:20.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell you don't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:23.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true! I really can juggle three!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:24.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:25.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:26.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:28.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm keeping watch right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:32.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your master is going to show you her expert skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:36.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a servant's duty to submit, and watch in awe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:37.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so unreasonable!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I order you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:40.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:45.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't order me as my master for\Nsomething like this! That's cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:48.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to make any more stupid promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:53.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Ouch, ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:55.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Stop biting me all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:58.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you always treat me so roughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:06.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then. I'll watch you, but make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:09.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you say things is always...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:11.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! All right! I want to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:14.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would love to have the honor of\Nseeing it, so please do it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As always, your words are insincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:22.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, I'm sure your attitude will change once you've watched me juggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally got the hang of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:31.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I learned the trick to it,\Nit was terribly simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:34.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm as good a juggler as Uraha now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:35.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:41.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I now understand how important it is to put all your heart and soul into doing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:42.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:43.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really did do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:24.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never said you were lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:27.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be watching, so just keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This time for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:33.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even experts can't do things well if they're nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:34.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:40.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:45.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See? See? I'm doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:52.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You did really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:54.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your consolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not trying to comfort you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:58.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to juggle like that because you tried really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:01.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not knowing when to give up is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:05.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell whether that's a compliment or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:06.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:09.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, you did well, Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:12.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:15.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as you practice every day, you'll become an expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:16.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:18.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:22.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you watch me juggle again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:25.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, if you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:29.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get some sleep while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a long walk today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:31.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to go over all these mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:54.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Going over the mountains is the best way to avoid our pursuers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.74,0:05:57.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to fetch some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me... please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:22.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't go in...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:25.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't go in, I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:31.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No more... please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't eat any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:40.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You'll catch a cold, sleeping like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:55.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't go back to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for the third time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:04.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuya-sama, that is not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:17.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt. What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:20.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna-sama, I am glad to see you in high spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:23.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like I'm in high spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:25.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you wake me up a little more gently?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, next time I shall adjust my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:32.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you to stop pulling my pillow away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:44.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have strange ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:47.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they get caught in\Nbranches when you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:52.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With such long ears, you must be able to hear things really far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:01.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you... How dare you tease me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:04.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up! Wait, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:06.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up! Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:08.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:09.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay still for a change!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:14.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:16.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a map I found at the market earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:18.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This was quite a find.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:21.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these wriggly marks like worms?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the names of rivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna, can't you read?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:28.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no one taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:30.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I can't read.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised Uraha let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:33.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:39.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna-sama told me that she would never learn to read, at least not from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:41.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:44.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you forgot about that incident with the poetry collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:47.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I only did that to enrich your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:50.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way my mind could be enriched with that teaching method!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:57.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At one time, I was teaching Kanna-sama poems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:09:00.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A little hardship always accompanies learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:02.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, Kanna-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:07.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Memorizing one hundred poems a day is 'a little' hardship to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:11.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There were 4500 poems in total, so we could not take our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:16.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't slept in five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:20.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You must continue until you've memorized two hundred more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:24.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:28.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would have been killed at that rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:31.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I threw all my poetry books into the stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:36.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, the six volumes of ancient poetry were used as fuel in the cooking of breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:40.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast that morning certainly had a poetic flavor to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:45.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those thoughtless words coming from this mouth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:47.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it, Uraha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:51.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A mouth that cannot recite a single poem is utterly useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:53.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is completely absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:55.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I might as well sew it shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:59.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:03.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm scared of Uraha too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:05.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You worthless fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:09.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:11.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost control of myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:13.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:15.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you the one excusing her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still talking funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:18.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to practice my juggling over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to go crazy over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:27.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:35.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you hitting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am taking it out on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:45.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:04.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A monk... isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:07.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably died from starvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:23.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuya-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:26.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:29.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Beanbags again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:31.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:35.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:37.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something on my mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:38.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:42.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's something you want to say, just come right out and say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:44.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something I want to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:49.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me say one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:50.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a caterpillar on top of your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:12:01.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Animals and bugs really seem to like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:03.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just sit there! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:07.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt that something might be wrong with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:10.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your master asked because she was concerned for her servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:11.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is what comes of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:13.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:15.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you, so just stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:18.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to tease me again, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:20.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not an interesting story though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:22.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really want to hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:23.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:28.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen my parents' faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:30.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:33.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I was abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:36.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An unsui took me in when he found me crying at the side of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An 'unsui' is a monk who travels around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:44.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Being called a 'traveling monk' might sound nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:48.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but in reality they wander homeless, surviving off charity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:52.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us traveled to many places together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:57.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We went north, south, east and west.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:01.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was your foster parent?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:03.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know if I could call him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:05.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was very strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:09.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless he was chanting prayers, he never opened his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:12.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He never even told me his monk name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:17.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was during the summer when I was about five years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:24.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Some bandits attacked us at a mountain pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:26.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The unsui was killed with a single swing of a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:32.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing that dead monk back there reminded me of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:36.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuya-dono, you had no mother either?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:37.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:42.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it's right for me to only search for my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:44.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what I want too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:53.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The unsui was still chanting a prayer even after he was slashed,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:56.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,praying that even those that killed him would still be able to go to heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:14:00.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he died, covered in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:03.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:07.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bandits said I wasn't even worth killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:11.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I was alone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:19.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I was alone for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.25,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:22.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did anything necessary to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.64,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:26.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I stole swords and spears, and took part in wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:27.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I even killed people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:31.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did everything I could just to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:34.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Until recently that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:35.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You could call it a change of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:44.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone can change, if given the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:49.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bandits must have deeply regretted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:50.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:53.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They killed a great monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they'd regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:59.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I truly doubt he was a great monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:01.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you doubt it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:07.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because his prayers were heard,\Nthe bandits didn't kill you. Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:15.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:20.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,True enough, maybe the unsui did save me back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:24.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had realized it sooner,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:26.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I might have taken a different path in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:28.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:31.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had, then I wouldn't have met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:36.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I met you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:39.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuya-dono...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:44.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuya-dono...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:47.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:48.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:49.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:53.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure what to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:59.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'll leave the rest up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:00.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:12.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:13.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:18.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, do you really know what I'm going to do to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:20.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take me for a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:22.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:24.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uraha told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew Uraha was behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:30.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... to me, you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:44.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uraha told me that when Ryuya-dono talks about his past, I shouldn't miss the opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:50.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All men talk of their past to the woman they love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:52.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:54.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She read me like a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:17:00.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And when he finishes talking, I am to slowly undress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:04.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's important to be sure that not all of my chest is visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.93,0:17:07.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an acting coach too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:15.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuya-dono, do you prefer men instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:16.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:18.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:22.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that there are some men who like women, but are impotent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:24.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:27.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I expose too much of my chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:28.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:33.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself. I will show you that I am a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:37.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuya-dono, you have a\Nstrange look in your eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:39.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's seducing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:41.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet and let me sink my venomous fangs into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have venom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:46.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All men do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:49.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a lot of things you don't even know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:53.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you everything you need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:56.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:17:59.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:03.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uraha! I know you're hiding around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:04.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:08.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, your intuition is quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:17.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna-sama, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:20.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know, but I think it didn't go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:22.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuya-dono...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:27.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I make you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:28.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:37.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uraha, you knew I wasn't going to touch her, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:40.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The odds were against me on this bet though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:42.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never find a more harmless man than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:45.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You could be called impotent as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:46.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:55.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sleeping well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:19:00.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was practicing with her beanbags quite a bit today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:04.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She does have a pretty cute face when she's like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to teach her the deceptions of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:09.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,before some strange men start making advances at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:11.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And you used me for practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:17.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't even played with dolls or beanbags before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:21.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:24.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.73,0:19:28.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:32.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't here, but a dream of another place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:36.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wearing strange clothes, and I looked different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:40.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it really me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:43.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:45.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:48.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mother was next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:50.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And other kind people were too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:54.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:57.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice dream, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:00.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just make that dream a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:03.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll meet your mother soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:06.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that dream won't be a dream anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.71,0:20:08.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:12.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I pray, I'm sure that my wish will reach the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:26.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:27.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:29.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still going!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:31.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still going!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:50.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You just need a little more practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:54.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was wonderful, Kanna-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.53,0:20:59.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep practicing a little more, you'll become even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:00.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:03.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I become good enough to show Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:05.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:18.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to go, Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:20.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:22.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:27.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:36.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:38.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:49.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you a long, happy life.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.07,0:00:31.22,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}We watched the fading vapor trails
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.77,0:00:35.67,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}They were so dazzling, I ran away
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.68,0:00:45.05,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}I was so frustrated, I released your hand
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.78,0:00:52.90,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}The place she can't reach is still there in the distance
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.66,0:00:59.98,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}She gazes at  it, keeping her wish to herself
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.29,0:01:08.43,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}Children walk along the summer railway tracks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.66,0:01:14.99,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}Holding in both hands their wishes to take flight
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.19,0:01:22.28,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}Chasing, chasing the fading vapor trails
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.15,0:01:29.93,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}It hasn't changed since the day we crossed that hill
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.93,0:01:32.19,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}And never will
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.26,0:01:38.33,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}And just as we are now, standing tall
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.83,0:01:47.24,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}We'll guard the strength of a sea god
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.42,0:01:52.34,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}Surely
